_sText:
My first map for CS:S. It's horrible.

I'm just getting into the modding scene and experimenting with Hammer. Even if you downright despise this map, feedback is always welcome.

Version 2 is no longer in development.
This is due to multiple reasons:
1. I don't even play CS:S that much, the only reason I made this map was for learning the basics behind Hammer.
2. A major bug regarding displacements was found on CT side, a bug I can't seem to fix. Every time I try to, it gets worse.

I may upload images of Version 2, but don't count on it.
This version of de_snowwatch however, will stay here, as it isn't as buggy/broken.
